OL,3,CPrison plans could cost 'extra #4bn
OL,4,Cand be short of 12,400 cell spaces by
OL,5,C2027'
OL,7,FA "damning" report from Whitehall's
OL,8,Fspending watchdog warns that the
OL,9,Fgovernment's plans to increase prison
OL,10,Fcapacity could fall short by thousands
OL,11,Fof cells within two years, costing
OL,12,Ftaxpayers billions more than expected.
OL,14,FThe National Audit Office (NAO) said
OL,15,Fcurrent expansion plans are
OL,16,F"insufficient to meet future demand,"
OL,17,Fwith a projected shortage of 12,400
OL,18,Fprison places by 2027 and costs
OL,19,Fexpected to exceed initial estimates
OL,20,Fby at least #4 billion.
