OL,7,FThe watchdog's report, published on
OL,8,FWednesday, blames the previous
OL,9,FConservative government for failing to
OL,10,Fensure that longer jail sentences and
OL,11,Fincreased police numbers were
OL,12,Fsupported by adequate prison space.
OL,14,FIt stated: "Years of under-investment
OL,15,Fin maintaining the prison estate put
OL,16,FMoJ and HMPPS in a weak position to
OL,17,Frespond to these increases."
