OL,7,FChief executive of the Prison Reform
OL,8,FTrust, Pia Sinha, described the
OL,9,Ffindings as "damning" and said they
OL,10,Flaid bare the "negligence of previous
OL,11,Fgovernments and their approach to
OL,12,Fpenal policy" which has left taxpayers
OL,13,Ffacing an "eye-watering bill with no
OL,14,Fcertainty on when the ongoing prison
OL,15,Fcapacity crisis will end".
