OL,3,CPrison plans could cost 'extra #4bn
OL,4,Cand be short of 12,400 cell spaces by
OL,5,C2027'
OL,7,FThe government's 2021 pledge to add
OL,8,F20,000 cell spaces is now expected to
OL,9,Fbe delayed until 2031, five years
OL,10,Flater than promised and only one-third
OL,11,F(6,518) has been made available so
OL,12,Ffar, according to the NAO.
OL,14,FDelays are due to "unrealistic
OL,15,Ftimelines" and overestimating the
OL,16,Fability to secure planning permission
OL,17,Ffor three of the six new prisons
OL,18,Fplanned for construction.
