OL,7,F"The Government must pull together a
OL,8,Fcoherent and viable long-term plan for
OL,9,Fa prison estate that meets demand and
OL,10,Fdelivers value for taxpayers' money,"
OL,11,Fhe added.
OL,13,FThe NAO also warned the government
OL,14,Fdepartment "does not have any
OL,15,Fcontingency plans to increase prison
OL,16,Fcapacity as it views it has limited
OL,17,Foptions left to do this".
