OL,7,FThe director of the Centre for Crime
OL,8,Fand Justice Studies, Richard Garside,
OL,9,Fdescribed governments and parliament
OL,10,Fas being "joint architects of a decade-
OL,11,Fin-the-making prisons crisis".
OL,13,FHe called on policy and lawmakers to
OL,14,F"set a fresh course, aimed at
OL,15,Fcontaining prison population growth in
OL,16,Fthe short-term and reducing it in the
OL,17,Fmedium to long-term".
