OL,3,CPrison plans could cost 'extra #4bn
OL,4,Cand be short of 12,400 cell spaces by
OL,5,C2027'
OL,7,FSince September, the government has
OL,8,Fbeen releasing thousands of inmates
OL,9,Fearly to reduce overcrowding,
OL,10,Ftemporarily lowering the proportion of
OL,11,Fsentences some prisoners must serve in
OL,12,FEngland and Wales from 50% to 40% but
OL,13,Fprisons are still expected to reach
OL,14,Fcritical capacity again by July.
OL,16,FMoJ figures show there were 86,059
OL,17,Fadult prisoners behind bars in England
OL,18,Fand Wales on Monday, slightly higher
OL,19,Fthan the 86,038 recorded at the
OL,20,Fbeginning of last week.
