OL,7,FThe latest data means the prison
OL,8,Fpopulation is only 2.8% lower than
OL,9,Fwhen the number of inmates being held
OL,10,Fhit a new record high of 88,521 on
OL,11,FSeptember 6, PA news agency analysis
OL,12,Fshows.
OL,14,FAn additional 1,350 cell spaces tend
OL,15,Fto always be kept free above the
OL,16,Foverall operational capacity of the
OL,17,Fprison estate in England and Wales as
OL,18,Fa contingency measure so jails can
OL,19,Fcope with a sudden influx of inmates
OL,20,For change in the make-up of the prison
OL,21,Fpopulation, according to the MoJ.
